The Lego Movie Videogame is an action-adventure video game developed by TT Games as part of the Lego series of video games. It follows the plot of the animated film The Lego Movie. The game was released by Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment alongside the film in 2014 for Microsoft Windows, Nintendo 3DS, PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita, Wii U, Xbox 360 and Xbox One, and on 16 October 2014 for Mac OS X by Feral Interactive
